Cell.Text: [S] G|Of course. Let me see if we have another bottle of that. | I'll be waiting by the door for everyone to be distracted.
[S] Here you go, sir. The finest Colovian brandy. | Is there anything else I can get for you?
[S] Here you go, ma'am. The finest Colovian brandy. | Is there anything else I can get for you?
We seem to have run out of Colovian brandy. I'll check in the wine cellar for more when I get a moment.
[S] Here you go, sir. Colovian brandy.
[S] Here you go, miss. Colovian brandy.
I'm sorry, but I think you've had enough for the moment.
G|Let me do the talking.
G|Not now.
G|Shut up, will you?
G|<<Shared>> Let's go, let's go! Before anyone notices us.
[S] What can I get for you? | You made it in. Good. As soon as you distract the guards, I'll open this door and we can get you on your way. | Let's hope we both live through this day.

Node.Caption: MQ201MalbornPartyBlockingTopic: I need to talk to you.

Cell.Text: G|Now the Thalmor will be hunting me for the rest of my life. I hope it was worth it.
G|I should have known this would end badly. I can't believe I let Delphine talk me into this.
G|Let's get out of here, for pity's sake!
G|Your job is to get into the party without being fingered as a spy. I'll take care of the rest.

S|Here's the deal. I can smuggle some equipment into the Embassy for you. | Don't plan on bringing anything else in with you. The Thalmor take security very seriously. | Give me what you can't live without, and I'll make sure to get it into the Embassy. The rest is up to you.
You ready yet? I need to get back before I'm missed. Remember, you won't have anything except what I smuggle in for you.
G|I'll give you a few more minutes. I can't wait here all day. It's my neck on the line, remember.

Node.Caption: MQ201MalbornEquipmentNotReady: Hold on, I need to get a few things ready.

Cell.Text: [S] G|Okay. I'll get this inside the Embassy for you. I've got to go. I'll find you at the party, don't worry.

Node.Caption: MQ201MalbornEquipmentReady: I'm ready. Here's what I'll need.

Cell.Text: [S] Really? You're who she picked? I hope she knows what she's doing.
You're asking me? She promised that she was sending someone who knew what they were doing... | If you actually want to get out alive, I'd bring whatever you need to move quietly, and kill quickly.

Node.Caption: MQ201MalbornEquipmentWhatToBring: What kinds of things should I bring?
